| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-5213 — Recovery Inhibition (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9dfa3e9d-2c76-541d-b792-89c1ea50da5e"
